      "title": "The European Union is delighted",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The European Union expressed its congratulations on reaching a staff agreement with Sri Lanka, the International Monetary Fund.",
        "The European Union said that it expects to provide Sri Lanka with the continued support of the European Union for public financial management and a green economy, including the export industry."
